@startuml
title Athena SDK Cookie Helpers (Before)

skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor Black
skinparam DefaultTextColor Black
skinparam Rectangle {
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

rectangle "Consumer App\n(Next.js middleware / proxy)" as consumer #F3F7FF
rectangle "@xylex-group/athena\n(current SDK surface)" as sdk #F8F8F8
rectangle "Athena Auth Server\n(Rust athena-auth runtime)" as server #FFF7E8

consumer --> sdk : import auth client
consumer --> consumer : manual cookie parsing\n(manual prefix / secure handling)
consumer --> server : request with cookie header
sdk --> server : auth API calls

note bottom of consumer
No dedicated `@xylex-group/athena/cookies` module.
Cookie parsing + cache inspection logic lives in app code.
end note
@enduml
